type: software
title: "plnt: multi-model inference playground on Kubernetes"
version: 0.1.0
date-released: "2026-07-14"
authors:
  - family-names: Talele
    given-names: Devdatta
    email: bonde.sagar@gmail.com
repository-code: "https://github.com/devdattatalele/plnt"
url: "https://plnt.work"
license: Apache-2.0
keywords:
  - kubernetes
  - inference
  - vllm
  - openai-compatible
  - helm
  - temporal
  - operator
  - nvidia
  - llm-serving
abstract: >
  plnt is an opinionated, Helm-native platform for deploying and serving
  multi-runtime ML inference on Kubernetes. It ships an OpenAI-compatible
  playground API, per-runtime Helm charts (vLLM, TGI, TRT-LLM, SGLang),
  a Temporal deploy saga, and an InferenceModel CRD driven by a Python
  operator.
